//
// This is a simple in-memory queue with optional persistence to disk.
// Notifications auto-expire after 24 hours.
//
// WHAT USES THIS:
//   core-chat.js  — queues "task completed" notifications
//   svc-pulse.js  — queues "chore finished" notifications
//   route-system.js — serves pending notifications to the front end
//
// EXPORTS:
//   queue(type, message, meta?)  — add a notification
//   poll(since?)                 — get notifications since timestamp
//   dismiss(id)                  — mark as read
//   clear()                      — remove all notifications
